   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Safe Water - Healthy Students - Improved Lives</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will install water filtration plants in 2 schools and provide safe drinking water to 821 children of rural area in Sindh. Lack of appropriate infrastructure has led to contamination of water reservoirs and local water supplies.The importance of providing safe drinking water to the children cannot be less emphasized. Also aims to address a secondary, but important goal of supporting the cause of education at the schools by limiting the incidence of waterborne diseases among students.</narrative>
  </description>
